data.title: Welcome to Suman Barik on Strikingly
data.text:
Name - Suman Barik

Nickname - Rony

Birthday - 29 December 2002

Nationality - Indian

Marital status - Unmarried

Currently live in - Kolkata, India

Education - Jadavpur High School

Native language - Bengali, Hindi, English

Hobbies - YouTuber, Tech Enthusiast, Vlogger

Hi, my name is Suman Barik aka Gadget Guru i was born in 29th December 2002 in Kolkata, India. i am 21 years old i live with my family and i have studied at Jadavpur High School in Kolkata, for the past 7 years I've been working as a junior artist at Bengali Television & Film Industry in Kolkata, i am a content creator on YouTube & Social Media, i worked in bengali serials as a junior artist which is known as Seema Rekha (zee bangla), Pratidaan (star jalsha), Mukhoser Araley (colors bangla) etc. and my main motive behind is being a youtuber is make something unique and knowledgeable content for everyone on Social Media.
